The paper deals with sketching algorithms and embeddings in metric and normed spaces, which are topics commonly studied in computer science subfields such as data structures (cs.DS), information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and computational complexity (cs.CC).
